                                                    <li>AADHAR</li>
                                                    <li>EMAIL ID</li>
                                                    <li>MOBILE NUMBER</li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        ANY ONE OF ELECTRICITY BILL / MOBILE BILL / TELEPHONE BILL / BANK STATEMENT MUST NOT
                                                        BE OLDER THAN 2 MONTHS*
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>PASSPORT SIZE PHOTOGRAPH</li>

                                                    <div>
                                                        <h3>For artificial persons following documents are required:</h3>
                                                        <p>
                                                            RESOLUTION FROM BOARD OF ARTIFICIAL PERSON
                                                        </p>
                                                        <br>
                                                        <h3>For address proof of company:</h3>
                                                        <p>
                                                            If owned premise: ANY ONE OF ELECTRICITY BILL / MOBILE BILL / TELEPHONE BILL MUST NOT
                                                            BE OLDER THAN 2 MONTHS* ALONG WITH NOC
                                                        </p>
