                                            <div class="acc__content">
                                                <p></p>
                                                <p>
                                                    A producer company is a company incorporated under Companies Act 2013 (formerly the
                                                    Companies Act 1956) and shall carry on following activities as mentioned in section 581B
                                                    of Companies Act 1956:
                                                </p>
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li>
                                                        Production, harvesting, procurement, grading, pooling, handling, marketing, selling,
                                                        export of primary produce of the Members or import goods for their benefit
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        Processing including preserving, drying, distilling, brewing, venting, canning and
                                                        packaging of produce of its members
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        Manufacture, sale or supply of machinery, equipment or consumables mainly to its
                                                        Members
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        Providing education on the mutual assistance principles to its Members and others
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        Rendering technical services, consultancy services, training, research and development
                                                        and all other activities for the promotion of interest of its members
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>
                                                        Generation, transmission and distribution of power, revitalization of land and water
